MAIN                  SECTION.                                   
P-010.                                                           
     DISPLAY "TEST START (EX4-2A)".                              
*>  ケース1.日本語データ（N）                                      
*>                                                                 
     MOVE "P-010-01"             TO CASE-ID.                     
     MOVE "あ" TO G-01.                                          
     IF G-01 = "あ"                                              
        AND FUNCTION BYTE-LENGTH(G-01) = 2                       
                                 DISPLAY CASE-ID "OK"            
        ELSE                     DISPLAY CASE-ID "NG"            
     END-IF.                                                     
